[30;1m361 | [0m[35m  - **used**: memory used, calculated differently depending on the platform and[0m

[30;1m181 | [0m[35m  Internally this function maintains a global map (a dict) where each key is[0m

[30;1m317 | [0m[35m    by using a Windows API that spawns a thread which keeps running in[0m

[30;1m170 | [0m[35m  before and after the interval (blocking).[0m

[30;1m176 | [0m[35m  at least ``0.1`` seconds between calls.[0m
